works.description:
This is Harun mala, Best for students  
doing higher studies,  for  their success in examination. This rosary is  

energized with Sarwaswati Mahamantra and Sampoteet Sri Mantra ,which makes
 
it very strong and after wearing this rosary , you will get success in  
educational sector everywhere. This rosary gives very sharp mind and
memory  
with that you can remember anything easily, it also  increases good luck  

and gives success in examinations.  For people in  educational sector,  
teachers, students going for higher studies it is best solution . It gives
 
success in everything which are related to education. If you have weak  
memory, you want to get success in examination,  any fear in mind, or you 

are teacher or running any educational institution -than you should wear  

this rosary in neck, so that you will get more students in institution and
 
also students  will get 1st position in the city, and make your education 

institution very famous. This rosary is most strong for education related 

problem, examination and educational business.
